\v 13 Coe⁴-ni³ ntˀai⁴ jon² xi³ vi³xon¹³: Ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ cao⁴ nchaon³-li⁴ cjoian¹ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹tse³ jan¹, jnco³ no¹ ya⁴ coi⁴yoa³², cˀoa⁴ coi⁴nta¹ tso³jmi², coi⁴njen⁴son²-na¹.  
