\v 7 Coi³ cjoa⁴-vi⁴ ˀnti¹ntsˀe³, cho¹ya³cao⁴cjoao⁴³ jo³ sa³ˀnta³ nca³ cjoa⁴ˀai¹ Nai³-na¹. Coe⁴-ni³ je² xi³ si¹xa¹jin³ na³nqui³ co³ya³-le⁴ tso³jmi²ntje² xi³ nˀion¹ chji¹-le⁴, xi³ tsjoa¹-le⁴ na³nqui³-ve⁴. Co³ya³cao⁴cjoa⁴-le⁴ jo³ sa³ˀnta³ nca³ cjoa⁴ˀai¹-le⁴ jtsi¹tjon² cao⁴ jtsi¹ xi³ scan³ ti⁴vˀa³-nca¹ni³.  
